snippet.title: 'Indie Dev Story' Trailer
snippet.description:
Available at
Itch.io :- https://cbgamedev.itch.io/indie-dev-story
GameJolt :- https://gamejolt.com/games/indie-dev-story/234888


Indie Dev Story - Quit your job to become an indie developer and make your first game.

A singleplayer 'clicker' game which tries to mimic the frantic feeling of being an indie developer; make your game while trying to stay healthy, social and earning enough money to pay the bills.

- How will your game do when it releases?
